1. Adding Live Sass compiler (vscode extension)
2. Creating folder .vscode (in project folder) --> settings.json
3. Creating sass folder --> main.scss (this is your main styles file, you will write all your styles in this file)
4. Connecting main.min.css in index.html


1. Variables:
    - the syntax for declaring variable is the $ sign before the name and its value after the colon : '$color: tomato;'
    - the usage example: 
        body {
            background-color: $color;
        }
